videos.description: Drick Bernstine feeds Conner Avants for the layup as UND takes a 6-5 lead . . . . Avants has all 6 points.
videos.headline: North Dakota's Avants on fire early

videos.description: Jerrick Hading makes the steal and goes all the way for the basket
videos.headline: Weber State's Harding converts defense into basket

videos.description: Jeremy Senglin pulls up and nails the 3-pointer to give WSU a 17-8 lead.
videos.headline: Senglin drains the deep 3

videos.description: Dusty Baker drives baseline and feeds Kyndahl Hill for the dunk.
videos.headline: Hill finishes with the jam

videos.description: Dusty Baker drives to the hoop and gets fouled and the basket.
videos.headline: Baker powers to the rim for the basket

videos.description: Corey Baldwin drains the 3-pointer and draws the foul as North Dakota cuts into lead.
videos.headline: Baldwin makes the 3 and draws the foul

videos.description: Corey Baldwin pulls up from the corner and nails the 3-pointer to pull North Dakota within 2 points.
videos.headline: Baldwin drains the 3

videos.description: Cortez Seales drives and makes the floater to give North Dakota a 45-40 lead.
videos.headline: Seales makes floater in the lane

videos.description: Jeremy Senglin hits the 3 to give Weber State a 56-52 lead.
videos.headline: Senglin 3-pointer extends Weber State lead

videos.description: Geno Crandall flips up the floater and draws the foul as North Dakota pulls within 72-67.
videos.headline: Crandell's driving layup gets North Dakota closer

videos.description: Kyndahl Hill grabs the miss and dunks to give Weber State a 79-75 lead late in game.
videos.headline: Hill follows up miss with the jam

videos.description: Quinton Hooker drives to the hoop and scores as North Dakota pulls within 81-79.
videos.headline: Hooker drives the lane for 2

videos.description: Geno Crandall gathers rebound and goes coast to coast to score game equalizer.
videos.headline: Crandall's last second layup sends game into OT

videos.description: Quinton Hooker drives the lane and scores to give UND an 83-81 lead.
videos.headline: Hooker floater gives UND overtime lead

videos.description: Geno Crandall drives and hits floater to give North Dakota an 89-86 lead.
videos.headline: Crandall hits clutch shot to beat shot clock

videos.description: North Dakota earns their first bid to the NCAA tournament after  93-89 win over Weber State.
videos.headline: North Dakota celebrates Big Sky championship

videos.description: Quinton Hooker excited to move onto NCAA tournament.
videos.headline: Quinton Hooker discusses big win over Weber State
